Description: PSR-7 and PSR-15 HTTP Basic Authentication Middleware
 Provides HTTP Basic Authentication middleware compatible with PSR-7
 and PSR-15 standards. Supports array and PDO-based authenticators,
 and flexible path/method routing rules.
